      <title>厄瓜多尔选民支持诺博亚的反黑手党措施，但拒绝他的经济改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ecuador-voters-back-noboa-s-anti-mafia-measures-but-reject-his-economic-reforms</link>
